import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import math

age = ["Di 20", "T 20 - di 25", "T 25 - di 30", "T 30 - di 35", "T 35 - di 50", "Trn 50"]
num_of_people_1971 = [118, 772, 288, 112, 112, 117]

fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 6))

def func(pct, num_of_people):
    absolute = int(np.round(pct/100.*np.sum(num_of_people_1971)))
    return "{:.1f}%\n({:d})".format(pct, absolute)

wedges, texts, autotexts = ax.pie(num_of_people_1971, autopct=lambda pct: func(pct, num_of_people_1971),
                                  textprops=dict(color="w"))

ax.legend(wedges, age,
          title=" tui",
          loc="center left",
          bbox_to_anchor=(1, 0, 0.5, 1))

plt.setp(autotexts, size=10)

ax.set_title(
    "S ngi nghin ma ty ti mt trung tm cai nghin vo nm 1971",
    fontsize=15,
    fontweight = 'bold',
    loc = 'center')
plt.show()

num_of_people_1972 = [96, 727, 376, 117, 118, 165]

# Cc ch s (index) cho cc thanh (bar)
ind = np.arange(len(age))

#  ln ca thanh 
width = 0.35

# V
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 6))

# V biu  thanh ngang
ax.barh(age, num_of_people_1972)
ax.set_xlabel('S ngi', fontweight = 'bold')
ax.set_ylabel(' tui', fontweight = 'bold')
ax.set_yticks(ind)
ax.set_yticklabels(age)

# Hm dn nhn cho cc thanh
def add_value_labels(ax, spacing=5):  
    # Vi mi thanh s t mt nhn
    for rect in ax.patches:
        # Xc nh v tr X, Y  t cc nhn
        x_value = rect.get_width()
        y_value = rect.get_y() + rect.get_height()/4

        # Khong cch gia thanh v nhn
        space = spacing

        # Dng x_value  lm nhn cho cc thanh
        label = "{:}".format(x_value)

        # To ch thch
        ax.annotate(
            label,                      # Dng label lm nhn
            (x_value, y_value),         # t label  bn tri cc thanh
            xytext=(space, 0),          # t lable cch thanh mt khong bng space
            textcoords="offset points") # Interpret `xytext` as offset in points

# Call the function above. All the magic happens there.
add_value_labels(ax)

ax.set_title(
    'S ngi nghin ma ty ti mt trung tm cai nghin vo nm 1972', 
    fontsize = 15,
    fontweight = 'bold',
    pad = 20,
    loc = 'center')
plt.show()

4. Nhn xt

Biu trn cho ta thy v s ngi nghin mt trung tm cai nghin nm 1971 v 1972.
Vo thi im ny, a s cc ngi nghin trung tm cai nghin ny nm trong tui t 20 n di 25 tui - chim hn 50% tng s ngi cai nghin. Hn na, khong 60% s ngi cai nghin ti trung tm ny nm tui di 25. iu ny cho thy nghin ngp l vn kh trm trng la tui thanh thiu nin.
cc nhm tui di 20 v t 20 n di 25, s ngi cai nghin c xu hng gim. cc nhm tui cn li th ngc li, c bit trong cc nhm tui t 25 n di 30 v trn 50 c xu hng tng mnh.

Cu 2 Bng sau l kt qu kho st lng thuc ht trung bnh mi ngy ca 68 ngi c ht thuc

S iu thuc ht trung bnh mt ngy [0;8) [8;12) [12;16) [16;24) [24;28) [28;34) [34; 50]
S lng 4 6 12 28 8 6 4
  1. Lp bng cho thy tn s (frequency), tn sut (relative frequency), mt (density), tn s tch ly (cumulative frequency), tn sut tch ly (cumulative relative frequency).
  2. V biu histogram.
  3. V biu tn sut tch ly.
  4. Nhn xt.

Bi lm

1. Lp bng cho thy tn s (frequency), tn sut (relative frequency), mt (density), tn s tch ly (cumulative frequency), tn sut tch ly (cumulative relative frequency).

In [4]:
# Cc khong
intervals = np.array([0, 8, 12, 16, 24, 28, 34, 50])

# S cc khong
num_of_intervals = len(intervals)-1

#  ln ca cc khong
intervals_width = np.diff(intervals)

# Tn s ca cc khong
frequency = np.array([4, 6, 12, 28, 8, 6, 4])

# Tn sut ca cc khong
probability = np.round(frequency/np.sum(frequency), 3)

# Mt 
density = np.round(np.array(probability/intervals_width), 3)

# Tn s tch ly
cumsum = np.cumsum(frequency)

# Tn sut tch ly
cumsum_prob = np.round(np.cumsum(probability), 3)


pd.DataFrame({
    "Interval":["{} - {}" .format(intervals[i], intervals[i+1]) for i in range(num_of_intervals)],
    "Frequency" : frequency,
    "Density" : density,
    "Relative Frequency": probability,
    "Cumulative Frequency": cumsum,
    "Cumulative relative frequency": cumsum_prob
})

1. Tnh trung bnh (mean), trung v (median), yu v (mode), phn v (percentile) 10%, 90%.

In [7]:
num_of_passengers = "165 141 163 153 130 158 119 187 185 209\
 177 147 166 154 159 178 187 139 180 143\
 160 185 153 168 189 173 127 179 163 182\
 171 146 174 149 126 156 155 174 154 150\
 210 162 138 117 198 164 125 142 182 218"
series_num_of_passengers = pd.Series([int(e) for e in num_of_passengers.split(' ')])

# Tnh trung bnh
mean = np.mean(series_num_of_passengers)
print('S hnh khc trung bnh trn mi chuyn tu l {}'.format(mean))

# Tnh trung v
median = np.median(series_num_of_passengers)
print('Trung v l {}'.format(median))

# Tnh yu v
import statistics as stat
mode = stat.multimode(series_num_of_passengers)
print('Yu v l {}'.format(mode))

# Tnh phn v 10%, 90%
percentile_0f_10, percentile_of_90 = np.percentile(series_num_of_passengers, [10, 90])
print('Cc phn v 10% l {} v 90% l {}'.format(percentile_0f_10, percentile_of_90))

S hnh khc trung bnh trn mi chuyn tu l 162.6
Trung v l 162.5
Yu v l [163, 153, 187, 185, 154, 182, 174]
Cc phn v 10% l 129.7 v 90% l 187.2

2. Tnh phm vi (range), khong t phn v (IQR - interquartile range), phng sai (variance), lch chun (standard deviation).

In [8]:
# Tnh phm vi
range = np.max(series_num_of_passengers) - np.min(series_num_of_passengers)
print('Phm vi l {}'.format(range))

# Khong t phn v (IQR - interquartile range)
lower_quartile, upper_quartile = np.percentile(series_num_of_passengers, [25, 75])
IQR = upper_quartile - lower_quartile
print('Khong t phn v l {}'.format(IQR))

# Phng sai
variance = np.var(series_num_of_passengers)
print('Phng sai l {}'.format(variance))

#  lch chun
std = np.std(series_num_of_passengers)
print(' lch chun l {}'.format(std))

Phm vi l 101
Khong t phn v l 31.25
Phng sai l 534.16
 lch chun l 23.11190169587955

Nhn xt

S ca nhim covid mi Vit Nam bt u tng trong khong thi gian t thng 6 nm 2021 v t cao tro thng 8,9 nm 2021. Thng 10 nm 2021, s ca nhim mi gim mnh. Sau li tng mnh tr li t thng 12 nm 2021 n hin nay. Tng s ca nhim hin nay l hn 200, 000 ngi.
Cng vi s ca nhim mi l s ngi cht v covid. T thng 7/2021 n nay, s ngi cht mi ngy dao ng trong khong t 100 n 800 ngi. Nng tng s ngi cht hin ti v covid ln n xp x 40, 000 ngi.

Nhn xt: T cc biu trn cho thy, dch covid bng pht Thi Lan sm hn Vit Nam. Dch bt u bng pht Thi Lan vo thng 4 nm 2021, sau pht tn mnh v t nh im thng 7 nm 2021. Sau s ca mi gim dn v cn di 5000 ca nhim trong mt ngy thi im thng 1 nm 2022. Tuy nhin s ca nhim mi ti Thi Lan ang c xu hng tng tr li. i vi Vit Nam, dch bt u bng pht sau Thi Lan khong 3 thng - thng 7 nm 2021. S ca nhim mi tng vt vo thng 8, 9 nm 2021 ri gim mnh vo thng 10. Sau s ca nhim mi tng mnh tr li.
Tng s ca nhim Vit Nam xp x tng s ca nhim Thi Lan. Tuy nhin, tng s ngi cht Vit Nam li gn gp i so vi Thi Lan.
